data.title: Film stars Clark Gable, Norma Shearer, Carole Lombard, and producer Louis B. Mayer walking to Jean Harlow's funeral service, Los Angeles, 1937
data.meta_description: Access to this collection is generously supported by Arcadia funds.Film stars Norma Shearer, Clark Gable, Carole Lombard, and producer Louis B. Mayer walking to Jean Harlow's funeral service. Harlow, known by many as "Baby," died suddenly of renal failure at age 26.Text from original nitrate sleeve: Jean Harlow Funeral; Shearer, Norma; Mayer, Louis B.; Lombard, Carole; Gable, ClarkHandwritten annotation from nitrate negative: Carole Lombard, Clark Gable
